      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NISTIRITH (4) led them up over this course and distance and bumped into a smart one again, beaten 1.8L. The form out of that race has been franked and there's nothing like Stylin' in this event. Can bounce back in a big way today. DEEPLY ROOTED (3) was too good last start, running over the top from midfield to score by 2.5L in impressive fashion. On the quick turnaround here and back slightly in trip, but that shouldn't be an issue with the aid of an inside draw. Just needs to run up to his latest effort to be winning again. DANCEWITHME (2) finished off nicely behind Stylin' last start when beating NISTIRITH at this track and trip 22 days ago. A better draw this time is a big tick with Fiore replacing the apprentice hoop. Can go one better. GOD'S WRATH (1) can sit handy from the draw and turn in a bold showing following a maiden win last time. ALOTOFBANTER (5) is best of the rest.",
